title: Morning Joe 8/25/21
description: President Joe Biden said Tuesday that the United States is on track to meet the current Aug. 31 deadline to withdraw troops from Afghanistan, leaving a narrow timeline to finish evacuating Americans and Afghan allies.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
